node.text:
We are excited to introduce our Brewing for Diversity Scholarship initiative in partnership with @ucsdextension and their brewing program! Ballast Point will grant one scholarship per year, and recipients will be selected by partner team members and the @sdbrewers Guild Inclusion Committee. We can’t wait to support YOU and a more inclusive brewing community. 

Visit the link in our bio for more information on how to apply!

node.text: Did you know Sculpin IPA was a recipe blend? Learn more about our iconic, award-winning IPA from the original brewers and our longtime label artist.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ballast Point Brewing Co. in San Diego, California. May be an image of 1 person, drink and outdoors.

node.text:
When the long weekend is treating you right 🙌🏽 🍻

Looking to make it even better? Pick up a Sculpin, Grapefruit Sculpin, or Swingin Friar Ale in our new 16oz cans. Because tbh those 4oz make a difference, and you deserve it.
